rightspotcdn.com/dims3/default/strip/false/crop/3542x1147+0+0/resize/1200/quality/85/format/webp/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fnpr-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F08%2Fb2%2F9bc89d9e402da503b7e6d1aa3237%2Frockwell-panels-all.png"target="_blank"   &gt;Click to enlarge.&lt;/a&gt;                 &lt;b class="credit" aria-label="Image credit"&gt;                                          Bruce M. White/The White House Historical Association                                      &lt;/b&gt;                 &lt;b class="hide-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;             &lt;/p&gt;         &lt;/div&gt;               &lt;b class="toggle-caption"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/b&gt;     &lt;/div&gt;       &lt;/div&gt;      &lt;/div&gt;    &lt;ol class="edTag"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Norman Rockwell's &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2026/06/25/nx-s1-5859276/norman-rockwell-so-you-want-to-see-the-president" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em&gt;So You Want to See The President!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is now on display for public viewing at The People's House in Washington, D.C. The suite of illustrations first appeared in &lt;em&gt;The Saturday Evening Post &lt;/em&gt;magazine in November 1943, at the height of World War II.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Meta plans to &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2026/06/24/nx-s1-5869486/meta-prediction-market-app-ai" target="_blank"&gt;launch a prediction market app&lt;/a&gt; called Arena to compete with companies like Kalshi and Polymarket. The new platform will allow users to wager on the outcomes of real-world events using "play money."&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;In this installment of Word of the Week, NPR explores &lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/2026/06/25/nx-s1-5863153/camp-word-history-military" target="_blank"&gt;how the term "camp" evolved&lt;/a&gt; from its origins in 16th-century military encampments into an integral part of American childhood, shaped by societal fears about modernity and masculinity.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;   &lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This newsletter was edited by &lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.npr.org/people/859721331/suzanne-nuyen"target="_blank"   &gt;&lt;em&gt;Suzanne Nuyen&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/div&gt;</description>
