      <title>UK PM Keir Starmer resigns. And, US and Iran agree to roadmap for final deal</title>
      <author>Brittney Melton</author>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2026/06/22/g-s1-129268/up-first-newsletter-keir-starmer-iran-us-vance-trump-reflection-pool</link>
